      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes the issues surrounding the timing of events in the rolling of a key in a DNSSEC-secured zone.  It presents timelines for the key rollover and explicitly identifies the relationships between the various parameters affecting the process.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
